OL,6,FPassing sentence at Sheffield
OL,7,FMagistrates Court on Wednesday 30
OL,8,FJuly, District Judge Tim Spruce
OL,9,Fordered the company to pay almost
OL,10,F#35,000 in costs on top of the fine.
OL,12,FHe said the fine would have been
OL,13,F#1.3million if the company had not
OL,14,Fadmitted the charge.
OL,16,FMr Spruce said: "Yorkshire Water's
OL,17,F#330 million profit before tax in 2025
OL,18,Fis not insignificant. Nor was the
OL,19,Fimpact on the Ingbirchworth dike.
