OL,3,CYorkshire Water fined #865k after
OL,4,Cpollution kills hundreds of fish
OL,6,F"This fine should have a real economic
OL,7,Fimpact to bring home to managers and
OL,8,Fshareholders the need to improve."
OL,9,Fsaid Judge Spruce.
OL,11,FThe Ingbirchworth treatment site
OL,12,Fprovides 90,000 people with drinking
OL,13,Fwater per day across Barnsley and
OL,14,FSouth Huddersfield.
OL,16,FHowever the water is toxic for fish.
