OL,3,CYorkshire Water fined #865k after
OL,4,Cpollution kills hundreds of fish
OL,6,FThe court heard that during the
OL,7,Fincident eight years ago, a faulty
OL,8,Fvalve which was opened manually was
OL,9,Fnot closed and this led to the water
OL,10,Fflowing into the dike.
OL,12,FThe Environment Agency said more than
OL,13,F400 dead fish were found on a single
OL,14,Fday of the incident.
