OL,6,FYorkshire Water's chief executive
OL,7,FNicola Shaw refused to comment after
OL,8,Fthe hearing but Yorkshire Water later
OL,9,Freleased a statement saying: "We take
OL,10,Four environmental responsibilities
OL,11,Fvery seriously and we apologise for
OL,12,Fthe harm that was caused by this
OL,13,Fincident.
OL,15,F"Since the incident, we've thoroughly
OL,16,Freviewed our processes and procedures
OL,17,Fto ensure this doesn't happen again at
OL,18,Fany of our sites.
