OL,6,F"We've also invested in improved
OL,7,Fmonitoring and equipment at
OL,8,FIngbirchworth water treatment works.
OL,10,F"Separately, we know our wider
OL,11,Fpollution performance hasn't been
OL,12,Fwhere it should be.
OL,14,F"We are investing #8.3 billion over
OL,15,Fthe next five years - an average of
OL,16,F#3.2 million every day - to improve
OL,17,Fservice levels, cut pollution and make
OL,18,FYorkshire's water infrastructure fit
OL,19,Ffor the future."
